title: Hour 1 - NFL Anticipation, Eli Manning
itunes:title: Hour 1 - NFL Anticipation, Eli Manning
description:
Dan looks forward to the NFL season kicking off tomorrow. Additionally, Super Bowl Champion and Emmy Award Winner, Eli Manning stops by to talk retirement, NFL action, and his brother Peyton.
